{"tid":2355138,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港版國安法｜正服刑黃之鋒亦遭查　警搜寓所1.5小時指涉違國安法","createTime":"2021-01-06T03:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T12:50:27.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b371c67761483249fbafe355c8bbd8fa56947d0a","tid":2355138,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:00:06.000Z","msg":"民主派去年發起初選爭取立法會「35+」，逾50名參加者今早（6日）遭警方國安處人員上門拘捕，被指涉嫌違國安法「顛覆國家政權罪」。<br />\n<br />\n其中在初選勝出的前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，目前因包圍警總案在石壁監獄服刑，其編輯在Fb表示，警方今晨以涉嫌違反《國安法》為由，到黃之鋒住所搜查近1.5小時。<br />\n<br />\n曾簽「抗爭聲明書」 初選高票勝出<br />\n黃之鋒去年7月參加民主派初選，在九龍東選區排首位高票出線，代表民主派參加立法會換屆選舉，但政府其後以疫為由取消選舉。<br />\n<br />\n「抗爭派」去年6月發起「墨落無悔 堅定抗爭」聲明書，當中提到若當選會運用《基本法》賦予立法會的權力，「包括否決財政預算案，迫使特首回應五大訴求，撤銷所有抗爭者控罪，令相關人士為警暴問責，並重啟政改達致雙普選」，黃之鋒當時有份簽署。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒FB指，警方今晨以涉嫌違反《國安法》為由，到黃之鋒住所搜查近1.5小時，由於黃之鋒目前正在石壁監獄服刑，或有可能在獄中被警方調查，律師團隊目前正在跟進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210106/423442767557955584824916.jpeg/aSxEeKy0YgHhRUAMwa1zeYQXR-1QNdiybWPLpG1jy6Q?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210106%2F423442767557955584824916.jpeg%2FaSxEeKy0YgHhRUAMwa1zeYQXR-1QNdiybWPLpG1jy6Q%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=aa3768a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"19a11db4dd2c0d66b25a35924dec2000f1c88c6f","tid":2355138,"uid":36995,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:04:28.000Z","msg":"Gphone慘到食兩舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872ab3068dc78670f47c080ed4248dfe60152545","tid":2355138,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:15:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a74b2e647afca92d30733e2d23a2556d54d263","tid":2355138,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T12:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}